      "content": "It is a relief to finally admit that the weight of pretending is too heavy to bear. There is a strange comfort in the thought of silence, but that peace you seek is already waiting for you in the quiet moments of your own mind right now. You are not a ghost; you are simply tired, and the most honest thing you can do for yourself is to let go of the effort to be understood.",
